-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Changes in version 0.17

- Added hooks to read previously hard-coded paths from $SRCMD_*
  environment variables.
- Adjusted SHA256 usage for new bglibs API.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Changes in version 0.14

- Modified srcmdd to set an alarm and kill the process.
- Added packet type validation in multiplex.c
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Changes in version 0.11

- Modified srcmdd to output input/output packet count/packet
  bytes/plaintext bytes statistics on exit.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Changes in version 0.10

- Modified srcmdd to report if the command was killed with a signal.
- Modified srcmdd to log the authenticated username.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
